title: Omotola Jalade-Ekeinde: Actress shares topless photo with husband
text: Nollywood screen diva, Omotola Jalade-Ekeinde just shared this photo of herself and husband topless! The couple are celebrating Valentine's day together topless and decided to let fans in on their shindig. " To all Osexynationals, Happy valentine from us. We love you, love someone, anyone today. #happyvalentinesday, " she wrote alongside it.
